Package: fermentR
Type: Package
Title: Converters and Calculators for Brewing and Fermentation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("whanrott", email = "will@oxfordbrewers.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
  )
URL: https://github.com/whanrott/fermentR/
BugReports: https://github.com/whanrott/fermentR/issues
Description: Converters and calculators for brewers of beer and other fermented
    drinks. May also be useful to people fermenting or testing the strength of sugar
    solutions such as honey. Calculations are from published information referenced
    in help files. Contains conversions for Brix, Specific Gravity, etc
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Suggests:
    birk,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
